		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: PPU Master/slave fear</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Theoretically it's possible that it might blow out the n-MOSFET pull-up drivers that're on the expansion port. But since these pins will never be used for anything unless you install something that uses them, you probably don't care.<br /><br />I have to think that if Nintendo actually had been concerned about damaging the PPU they'd've put resistors to ground on the lines rather than simply tying them low.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


